OL,3,CPolice constable charged with causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA police officer has been charged with
OL,7,Fcausing death by dangerous driving
OL,8,Ffollowing a fatal crash in Bristol
OL,9,Fcity centre nearly three years ago.
OL,11,FThe police constable was pursuing a
OL,12,Fcar that had failed to stop when it
OL,13,Fhit a Honda Jazz in Newfoundland
OL,14,FCircus in November 2021.
OL,16,FThe Honda driver died in hospital.
OL,18,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,19,FConduct investigated the incident
OL,20,Fafter Avon and Somerset Police
OL,21,Freferred itself to the watchdog.
