OL,6,FIn a statement, the IOPC said: "We
OL,7,Fdecided to investigate after receiving
OL,8,Fa mandatory referral from Avon and
OL,9,FSomerset Police in November 2021.
OL,11,F"Following the end of our
OL,12,Finvestigation we sent a file of
OL,13,Fevidence to the Crown Prosecution
OL,14,FService (CPS) for consideration of any
OL,15,Fpotential criminal offence.
OL,17,F"The CPS subsequently authorised the
OL,18,Fcharge.
