OL,6,F"We have been advised by the officer's
OL,7,Frepresentatives that they are applying
OL,8,Fto the court to keep their identity
OL,9,Fanonymous, so we are unable to name
OL,10,Fthe officer at this stage."
OL,12,FThe 38-year-old police constable is
OL,13,Fdue to appear at Bristol Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt on Thursday 12 September.
